<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8235449>
    dc:description "Fig. 5. Antidiabetic effects of A. villosum on db/db mice, (A–E) random blood glucose (0–4 weeks), (F) fasting blood glucose (4th week), (G) plasma insulin level, (H) plasma leptin level, (I) OGTT, (J) ITT, (K) food intake, and (L) body weight. Data were presented as mean ±SDs (n =8). *p <0.05, **p <0.01 vs Vehicle, ##p <0.01, ###p <0.001, ####p <0.0001 vs Lean." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8235449/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8235451>
    dc:description "Fig. 6. The stimulation of fractions and compounds on GLP-1 secretion. Oleoylethanolamide (OEA) was used as positive control. Data were expressed as mean ± SD (n = 3). **p <0.01, ***p <0.001." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8235451/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

